history.content:
Hi guys, take a look at this amazing opportunity!

Armstrong, the Daher innovation program based in San Francisco, is co-hosting an amazing innovation competition with Robomaster at Berkeley around Daher aircraft, the TBM: The General Aviathon. http://bit.ly/Aviathon

1 stunning product, 2 challenges to participate in:

Advanced Features: give some intelligence to our aircraft
User Experience: improve the experience and services around the TBM

WHY? A chance to pitch your idea at the National Business Aviation Association (NBAA) Conference and Exhibition in Las Vegas this October; a potential industrialization of your idea with Daher and Microsoft; 2x5000$ to win & many other perks!

WHO? Whether you are an aviation lover, an engineering student, a business guy, or ANYONE, Daher warmly encourages you to think about YOUR way to build the #FutureOfAviation.

Visit the website for more details and submit your idea! http://bit.ly/Aviathon

Do not hesitate to get in touch with Daher at TheGeneralAviathon@daher.com or Robomaster at Berkeley at robomasteratberkeley@gmail.com for more details!

CLICK THE LINK TO SUBMIT YOUR IDEA.
